    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. The exterior retains a great luster, though you will find some typical minor scratches and a few small stone chips consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with the upholstery showing only light wear and all electronic features functioning as they should. Mechanically, the car is sound, having received regular oil changes and scheduled servicing, ensuring a smooth driving experience for years to come.",
