    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone on a budget. The engine and transmission are functional, though you may notice some typical wear-and-tear such as minor fluid seeps or aged suspension components. The exterior has some visible scratches and paint fading, and the interior shows signs of regular use. It is a solid, roadworthy car that would benefit from some cosmetic detailing and routine maintenance to keep it running well.",
