    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards. With its flawless finish and pristine interior, it offers a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is an acquisition for the discerning collector who demands nothing short of perfection.",
