      "description": "Presented in concours-level condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior, has been meticulously maintained to meet the most exacting standards. Mechanically superlative and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this specimen offers an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning collector who demands excellence without exception.",
      "price": 48500.0,
